title: County Parks and Parkway Lands, Westchester County New York, 2004
name: County Parks and Parkway Lands, Westchester County New York, 2004
description: This data layer consists of County-owned Parks and Parkway Lands and  is a result of a comprehensive county-wide update to the 1994 major open spaces GIS data layer and map. The layer was derived from the "wcospace" layer which serves as the master coverage of all county open space. A variety of sources were used to compile this information, including aerial photography, digital tax parcel data, and local recreation, land use and master plan maps. Other sources included municipal planning departments and consultants, conservation committees and the Westchester Land Trust.
